TextEng: Who are you?
I have some questions.
What seems to be the problem?
Fine, I'll go.
Who you?
Me has questions.
What is big problem?
Okays, me go.
At least tell me who you are, then.
Why? What's wrong?
I see. You're too good to talk to me, is that it?
Say who you is, then.
Why? What be wrong?
Me sees. You be too gooder to talk to me, huh?
Text: 알았어. 너 나한테 얘기하기 너무 좋은 거지?

TextEng: What happened?
Aww... poor rich noble lost all her gold?
Text: 아이고... 불쌍한 부자 귀족이 금화를 전부 잃었네?

TextEng: You lost your title? That isn't everything.
I'm going now.
What happen?
Aww... poor rich girlie lose all gold, huh?
Text: 아이고... 불쌍한 부자 여자가 금화 다 잃었네?

TextEng: You loses name? Is okay, me loses name lots.
Text: 이름 잃었어? 괜찮아, 나도 이름 많이 잃어.

TextEng: Me go now.
Sure you would.
Uh-huh. It be bad story, me thinking.
That is very sad.
Sounds like a tough break.
Hah! At least you're still alive.
That be very sad.
It be tough break for you.
Pfaw! You is alive, no?
Perhaps I could help.
Text: 내가 도와줄 수 있을 것 같은데.

TextEng: I could help... for the right reward.
Text: 도와줄 수는 있어... 적당한 보상이 있다면.

TextEng: Yes, well, life's tough all over.
Text: 그래, 뭐, 인생은 어디든 힘든 법이지.

TextEng: Maybe me could helps.
Me help... for good reward.
Yeah, well... life be tough.
Text: 그래, 뭐... 인생 원래 힘든 거야.

TextEng: Tell me where it is now and I'll do it.
Text: 지금 어디 있는지 말해 줘, 그럼 할게.

TextEng: Very well... I'll help you.
I'll do what I can.
I changed my mind. Not interested.
Tell me where is now and me helps.
Text: 지금 어디 있는지 말해 줘, 그럼 도와줄게.

TextEng: Okays, me helps you.
Me do what me can, then.
Me changing mind. Have no interest.
Where can I find Baram?
Do you know where your children might be?
Why would Baram be holding your children?
Text: 왜 바람이 아이들을 데리고 있는 거야?

TextEng: Does Baram have any enemies?
I'll go now.
Where me finds this Baram?
You knows where kids be?
Why Baram keeps kids?
Baram has enemies, maybe?
Me go now.
I have found nothing yet, but I hope to.
Text: 아직 아무것도 못 찾았지만, 찾을 거야.

TextEng: Me knows nothing yet, but soon.
Text: 아직 아무것도 모르는데, 곧 알 거야.

TextEng: I'll get around to it.
Me gets around to it, maybe.
I have spoken to Baram... He says your children are safe.
Me talks to Baram... He says kids is okay.
Text: 나 바람이랑 얘기했어... 애들 괜찮다고 했어.

TextEng: Baram has reneged on his deal. He will not release your children.
Text: 바람이 약속을 어겼어. 아이들을 풀어주지 않겠대.

TextEng: Baram brokes his deal. He not lets kids go.
Text: 바람이 약속 깼어. 애들 안 풀어줘.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Your children are fine, Londa... but I can't bring them to you.
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 아이들은 괜찮아, 론다... 하지만 데려올 수는 없어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> The kids is okay. Me can no bring them, though.
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 애들 괜찮아. 근데 나 못 데려와.

TextEng: I am sorry, Londa. All your children are dead...
Me is sorry, Londa. All the kids is dead...
They're dead, actually. Baram and his rats ate them.
Text: 사실 죽었어. 바람이랑 쥐들이 먹어 치웠어.

TextEng: They is dead. Baram and rats eats them all up.
I have agreed to perform a service for Baram in return for their release.
Text: 바람이 풀어주는 대가로 일을 해주기로 했어.

TextEng: Me going to do stuff for Baram, then he let kids go.
Text: 나 바람 위해 일 할 거야, 그럼 애들 풀어준대.

TextEng: Baram wanted me to kill Kurth for their release, but I refused.
Text: 바람이 풀어주는 대신 커스를 죽이라고 했는데, 거절했어.

TextEng: Baram want me to kills Kurth for kids, but me say no.
Text: 바람이 애들 위해 커스 죽이래, 근데 나 싫다고 했어.

TextEng: I'll see what I can do.
Me do what me can.
No, I have no idea.
No, me haves no clue.
The small ones. The rest he turned into wererats... and they're dead, too.
Text: 어린 아이들. 나머지는 시궁쥐인간으로 만들었어... 그것들도 죽었고.

TextEng: Small ones. Others he makes wererats. Me kills them.
Text: 작은 애들. 나머지는 시궁쥐인간 됐어. 나 죽였어.

TextEng: It's the truth. I thought you should know.
It be truth. Me thinks you shoulds know.
Text: 진짜야. 너 알아야 할 것 같아.

TextEng: (yawn!) You'll get over it.
(yawn!) You gets over it, me thinking.
Baram... sent them away. To orphanages, elsewhere. I don't know where they are.
Text: 바람이... 아이들을 보냈어. 고아원으로. 어디 있는지는 모르겠어.

TextEng: Baram... send kids away. To orphanages. Me not know where.
Text: 바람... 애들 보냈어. 고아원으로. 나 어디 있는지 몰라.

TextEng: I can't lie to you, Londa. Your children are dead...
Text: 거짓말할 수 없어, 론다. 아이들은... 죽었어...

TextEng: I no want lies, Londa. The kids is dead...
Text: 나 거짓말 안 해, 론다. 애들... 죽었어...

TextEng: Fine, make me tell the truth. Baram and his rats ate your kids.
Text: 좋아, 진실을 말해줄게. 바람이랑 쥐들이 아이들을 먹어 치웠어.

TextEng: (sigh) Okay, me say truth. Baram and rats eats the kids.
Text: (한숨) 좋아, 진실 말할게. 바람이랑 쥐들이 애들 먹었어.

TextEng: Very well. I shall return.
Okay. Me comes back, then.
Forget it. I don't care if you don't believe me.
You forget it! Me no care if you not believing!
Text: 됐어! 나 신경 안 써, 안 믿으면!

TextEng: Look... I just want the coin. That's all.
Text: 보자... 난 그냥 돈이 필요해. 그게 다야.

TextEng: Me wants coin. You give me.
Hand over the coin or you'll join your husband... get it?
Text: 돈 내놓지 않으면 남편을 만나게 될 거야... 알겠어?

TextEng: You gives me coin or you meets husband!
Text: 돈 줘, 안 그럼 남편 만나!
